From main directory:
```
mkdir build
cd build
cmake ..
make
```

To use magma:
```
cmake -DBUILD_FOR_GPU=ON -DCMAKE_EXE_LINKER_FLAGS="${CUDA_LIB} -lcudart -lcudadevrt -lcublas -lcusparse" ..

(or call scripts/condo_gpu_cmake)

Note: the appropriate modules may need to be loaded (openBLAS, cuda, magma,...)
